@startuml Happy Path — OFFERED → SETTLED
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

title Happy Path: Contract Lifecycle\nOFFERED → NEGOTIATING → SIGNED → ACTIVE → DELIVERED → SETTLED

actor Seller
actor Buyer
participant "API Gateway" as GW
participant "product-service" as PS
participant "contract-service" as CS
database "contract_db\n(+ outbox)" as CDB
participant "Outbox Poller" as OP
queue "RabbitMQ" as MQ
participant "escrow-service" as ES
participant "notification-service" as NS

== 1. Seller tạo Listing ==
Seller -> GW : POST /api/listings
GW -> PS : forward
PS -> PS : Listing.create() [ACTIVE]
PS --> Seller : 201 listingId

== 2. Buyer tạo Offer ==
Buyer -> GW : POST /api/contracts\n{listingId, proposedTerms}
GW -> CS : forward (X-User-Id: buyerId)
CS -> CS : Contract.offer() → OFFERED
CS -> CDB : save contract
CS --> Buyer : 201 contractId

== 3. Đàm phán (0..n lần) ==
note over Seller, CS: Cả hai bên có thể counter-offer\nMỗi lần append NegotiationEvent\nContract ở NEGOTIATING sau counter-offer đầu tiên

== 4. Hai bên ký Contract ==
note over Seller, Buyer: Mỗi bên gọi sign() riêng.\nSau lần ký đầu: vẫn OFFERED/NEGOTIATING.\nSau lần ký thứ hai (cả hai đã ký): → SIGNED

Seller -> GW : PUT /api/contracts/{id}/sign
GW -> CS : forward (X-User-Id: sellerId)
CS -> CS : Contract.sign(sellerId)\nAdd sellerId vào signatories set\nchưa đủ 2 — giữ nguyên state
CS --> Seller : 200 OK

Buyer -> GW : PUT /api/contracts/{id}/sign
GW -> CS : forward (X-User-Id: buyerId)
CS -> CS : Contract.sign(buyerId)\nsignatories.size() == 2 → SIGNED
CS -> PS : PUT /listings/{id}/close [OpenFeign SYNC]
PS -> PS : Listing.close() [ACTIVE → CLOSED]
PS --> CS : 200 OK
CS -> CDB : save contract + ContractSignedEvent (PENDING)
CS --> Buyer : 200 OK

== 5. Outbox Poller publish ==
OP -> CDB : SELECT WHERE status=PENDING
CDB --> OP : [ContractSignedEvent]
OP -> MQ : publish routing-key: contract.signed
OP -> CDB : UPDATE status=PUBLISHED

== 6. Escrow lock (async) ==
MQ -> ES : contract.signed
ES -> ES : check contractId idempotency\n(nếu đã LOCKED thì skip)
ES -> ES : EscrowAccount.lock()\nDeduct mock buyer balance → LOCKED
ES -> MQ : publish escrow.locked

== 7. Contract → ACTIVE (async) ==
MQ -> CS : escrow.locked
CS -> CS : Contract.activate() → ACTIVE
CS -> CDB : save

== 8. Notification (async) ==
MQ -> NS : escrow.locked
NS -> NS : check eventId idempotency
NS -> NS : send email to seller
note right of NS : "Buyer đã lock escrow\nTiến hành giao hàng"

== 9. Buyer xác nhận nhận hàng ==
Buyer -> GW : PUT /api/contracts/{id}/confirm-delivery
GW -> CS : forward (X-User-Id: buyerId)
CS -> CS : Contract.confirmDelivery(buyerId) → DELIVERED
CS -> CDB : save + ContractDeliveredEvent (PENDING)
CS --> Buyer : 200 OK

OP -> MQ : publish contract.delivered

== 10. Escrow release (async) ==
MQ -> ES : contract.delivered
ES -> ES : EscrowAccount.release()\nLOCKED → RELEASED\nAdd mock seller balance
ES -> MQ : publish escrow.released

== 11. Contract → SETTLED (async) ==
MQ -> CS : escrow.released
CS -> CS : Contract.settle() → SETTLED
CS -> CDB : save

== 12. Notification (async) ==
MQ -> NS : escrow.released
NS -> NS : send email to both parties
note right of NS : "Escrow released\nHop dong da SETTLED"

@enduml
